title: EU-Singapore free trade deal exposes EU falsity over Brexit - William Dartmouth MEP
description:
• European Parliament, Strasbourg, 12 February 2019

• William Dartmouth MEP  (South West), Europe of Freedom and Direct Democracy group (EFDD) http://www.williamdartmouth.com

• Joint Debate: EU-Singapore Partnership Agreement

1. EU-Singapore Free Trade Agreement
Recommendation:  David Martin (A8-0053/2019)
Recommendation on the draft Council decision on the conclusion of the Free Trade Agreement between the European Union and the Republic of Singapore
[07971/2018 - C8-0446/2018 - 2018/0093(NLE)]
Committee on International Trade

2. EU-Singapore Free Trade Agreement (resolution)
Report:  David Martin (A8-0048/2019)
Report containing a motion for a non-legislative resolution on the draft Council decision on the conclusion of the Free Trade Agreement between the European Union and the Republic of Singapore
[2018/0093M(NLE)]
Committee on International Trade

3. EU-Singapore Investment Protection Agreement
Recommendation:  David Martin (A8-0054/2019)
Recommendation on the draft Council decision on the conclusion on behalf of the European Union of the Investment Protection Agreement between the European Union and its Member States, of the one part, and the Republic of Singapore, of the other part
[07979/2018 - C8-0447/2018 - 2018/0095(NLE)]
Committee on International Trade

4. EU-Singapore Investment Protection Agreement (resolution)
Report:  David Martin (A8-0049/2019)
Report containing a motion for a non-legislative resolution on the draft Council decision on the conclusion on behalf of the European Union of the Investment Protection Agreement between the European Union and its Member States, of the one part, and the Republic of Singapore, of the other part
[2018/0095M(NLE)]
Committee on International Trade

5. EU-Singapore Partnership and Cooperation Agreement
Recommendation:  Antonio López-Istúriz White (A8-0020/2019)
Recommendation on the draft Council decision on the conclusion, on behalf of the European Union, of the Partnership and Cooperation Agreement between the European Union and its Member States, of the one part, and the Republic of Singapore, of the other part
[15375/2018 - C8-0026/2019 - 2018/0403(NLE)]
Committee on Foreign Affairs

6. EU-Singapore Partnership and Cooperation Agreement (resolution)
Report:  Antonio López-Istúriz White (A8-0023/2019)
Report containing a motion for a non-legislative resolution on the draft Council decision on the conclusion, on behalf of the European Union, of the Partnership and Cooperation Agreement between the European Union and its Member States, of the one part, and the Republic of Singapore, of the other part
[2018/0403M(NLE)]
Committee on Foreign Affairs
